# __SPECX_PROJECT_NAME__

A framework-neutral Python project initialized with Specx. It starts with a
small `core/health` use case and service composed through `ioc/container.py`.
No delivery framework is selected.

## Setup

```bash
uv sync --all-groups
make check
```

The health slice is the example for adding further scoped core behavior. Add
technology-specific delivery and infrastructure only when the project needs them.
